Manage file index

Usage: moss index [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>

Commands:
  rebuild   Rebuild the file index
  stats     Show index statistics (DB size vs codebase size)
  files     List indexed files (with optional prefix filter)
  packages  Index external packages (stdlib, site-packages) into global cache
  help      Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -r, --root <ROOT>  Root directory (defaults to current directory)
      --json         Output as JSON
      --jq <EXPR>    Filter JSON output with jq expression (implies --json)
      --pretty       Human-friendly output with colors and formatting
      --compact      Compact output without colors (overrides TTY detection)
  -h, --help         Print help
